snippet.textDisplay:
Am compelled to appreciate especially the background music of this divine experience! 
With that curius, sweet-sour flute, it sets the stage for knowledge to come, and then each moment brings us closer to the light! Finally attaining bliss, dukh bhi apne sukh bhi apne, tu bas jhoom! Those chords: they express the satisfaction, the tears of ecstasy. 
Am grateful for coke studio for providing such an experience.
